<span class="postbody">There is a crazy cat lady that lives between Goldshire and the newbie zone to the north.  You can buy a cat carrier from here.
<br />

<br />
The only kitten I know of as a permanent in-game map is purchaseable from an NPC named Timmy or something that roams throughout Stormwind.  It is a limited vendor item (meaning if someone buys one, it will be a while before another one is available).  Unlike limited recipes which seem to refresh rather quickly, it is rumored that the white kitten carrier may take much longer to refresh.
<br />

<br />
I have seen this item in-game at the Gadgetzan AH, so I know it exists.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
